channel.title: Need help portforwarding!
channel.description:
I followed many portforwarding tutorials,and i think i did everything right but i still can't play my rsps. I got a 728 rsps,all ports are 43594,i changed the ip adress to my no-ip one, In my router (d-link 635) i opend port 43594 in tcp and udp. in the ip adress box,i putted my ipv4 adress,and i made my port name RSPS. my schedule is set on always,and my inbound filter on allow all. It's also not because of the firewall because i putted it off for a second,and it still didnt work.
could someone help? :/
